{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"dd8ae32cafe73d1af985f4c62181ab12bcad03b50148894987c0f5ff38da1343","slug":"qtcloud-data","location":"/archive/roadmap/products/qtcloud/qtcloud-data.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"量潮数据云","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech","keywords":["quanttide","documentation"],"numbering":{"title":{"offset":4}},"source_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/blob/main/docs/archive/roadmap/products/qtcloud/qtcloud-data.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/edit/main/docs/archive/roadmap/products/qtcloud/qtcloud-data.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"qtcloud-data.md","url":"/qtcloud-data-f24173b1ac1b9f4c067b122b0052fc30.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"量潮云数据工程平台，简称量潮数据云，是一站式数据工程管理协作平台。","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"iKZY3WwwRU"}],"key":"pXRz26HpTc"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在“数据工程”领域，我们的平台专注于构建、维护和管理数据基础设施，包括支持数据的收集、存储、处理、转换和传输，以满足数据分析、业务洞察和决策支持等需求。“管理”指管理者和数据工程团队统一治理数据基础设施和管理数据分析团队的工作；“协作”指数据工程与分析团队内部和团队间的协同工作。作为一个“平台”，我们以平台即服务（PaaS）的形式为客户提供云端服务，通过云原生架构降低边际使用成本并提高可用性，从而帮助客户减轻基础设施管理负担；此外，我们还提供一系列开源库和开发者工具，帮助客户降低使用门槛。“一站式”意味着我们的平台可以满足数据工程领域的所有管理和协作需求；通过提供一套完整的工具和功能，我们致力于简化数据工程流程的每个环节，帮助客户优化数据工程任务的执行。","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"key":"i2gp5vv18O"}],"key":"qAL9mtaajo"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"用户画像","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"ulE4Lb8JhC"}],"identifier":"id","label":"用户画像","html_id":"id","implicit":true,"key":"i4Z6S9cAfG"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":12,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我们将用户分为三类角色：数据工程师、数据分析师和管理者。\n数据工程师是数据工程领域的专业人士，他们在组织内负责设计和实施数据架构、数据流水线以及数据处理系统。他们致力于确保数据在组织内部的高效、安全和可靠的流动和使用。\n数据分析师是负责进行数据分析和挖掘的专业人士，他们通过对数据的深度分析和解读，为组织提供决策支持和业务洞察。数据分析师利用统计和分析技术，结合业务知识，从数据中发现趋势、模式和关联，并将其转化为可理解的报告和可视化结果。\n管理者是组织中负责数据工程和数据分析团队的领导者，他们负责整体的数据工程和分析策略规划以及团队管理。管理者需要协调和管理数据工程师和数据分析师之间的协作，确保数据基础设施和数据分析工作的高效运作。","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"JrVRe6yBfP"}],"key":"mqMifkWiyC"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1},"end":{"line":14,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"数据工程师","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1},"end":{"line":14,"column":1}},"key":"II3LeItRx0"}],"identifier":"id","label":"数据工程师","html_id":"id-1","implicit":true,"key":"BTbsb7zQQh"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1},"end":{"line":16,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"作为数据工程师，他的职责是设计和实施数据架构、数据流水线和数据处理系统。他致力于确保数据在组织内部的高效、安全和可靠的流动和使用。","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1},"end":{"line":16,"column":1}},"key":"znGJntczBw"}],"key":"EewY4rdkcb"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":1},"end":{"line":18,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"为了在这个角色中表现出色，他需要具备数据建模、ETL工具、数据库管理、编程和脚本语言等方面的技能。了解最新的数据处理技术、数据架构设计指南以及数据质量和性能优化技巧是非常重要的。","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":1},"end":{"line":18,"column":1}},"key":"pUIx7Nwola"}],"key":"zxFrdejODN"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"通常情况下，数据工程师通常具备计算机科学、数据科学或相关领域的学士或硕士学位。此外，具备相关的数据工程和架构培训或认证也会被视为加分项。","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"key":"razMNM7kvl"}],"key":"V1qlRVZHGH"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"他通常需要具备数年的数据工程经验，参与过数据架构和处理系统的设计和实施。具备处理大规模数据和数据流水线的经验会被优先考虑。","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"key":"b5kehAjswU"}],"key":"OesQprCSf7"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1},"end":{"line":24,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"数据工程师可以在各种规模和行业的组织中工作，包括但不限于科技、金融、零售和制造业。他的工作环境可能涉及与多个团队和部门的合作，需要良好的沟通和协调能力。","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1},"end":{"line":24,"column":1}},"key":"iN1n0Epx67"}],"key":"qUohtdbVyE"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":26,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"他需要熟练使用数据建模工具（如Erwin、PowerDesigner）、ETL工具（如Informatica、Talend）、数据库管理系统（如Oracle、SQL Server、MySQL）以及编程和脚本语言（如Python、Java、Shell）。","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":26,"column":1}},"key":"BWBlk4U5Y5"}],"key":"cReXK2Qt5h"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1},"end":{"line":28,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在这个角色中，他可能面临处理大规模和多样化数据、确保数据质量和一致性、提高数据处理和查询性能等挑战。为了满足这些挑战，他需要掌握最新的数据处理技术、数据架构设计的最佳实践以及数据质量和性能优化的技巧。","position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1},"end":{"line":28,"column":1}},"key":"EJH1VGWyUf"}],"key":"zqMW35Aog4"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1},"end":{"line":30,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"产品特性","position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1},"end":{"line":30,"column":1}},"key":"G25YNMV4F6"}],"identifier":"id","label":"产品特性","html_id":"id-2","implicit":true,"key":"IhYGgIbrs2"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":1},"end":{"line":32,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"数据集和数据应用管理","position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":1},"end":{"line":32,"column":1}},"key":"zXex3Pk1ud"}],"identifier":"id","label":"数据集和数据应用管理","html_id":"id-3","implicit":true,"key":"EgKaC9aoCX"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1},"end":{"line":34,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"数据处理程序管理","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1},"end":{"line":34,"column":1}},"key":"GkFknScgLl"}],"identifier":"id","label":"数据处理程序管理","html_id":"id-4","implicit":true,"key":"nEy96SXxA1"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":36,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"数据处理流程编排","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":36,"column":1}},"key":"nZZksntc3r"}],"identifier":"id","label":"数据处理流程编排","html_id":"id-5","implicit":true,"key":"wScA6l05VV"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"研发流程管理","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"key":"mEugEWQE48"}],"identifier":"id","label":"研发流程管理","html_id":"id-6","implicit":true,"key":"HyXvLKSTnx"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":1},"end":{"line":40,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"数据安全治理","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":1},"end":{"line":40,"column":1}},"key":"BeVDzvX3Qk"}],"identifier":"id","label":"数据安全治理","html_id":"id-7","implicit":true,"key":"GIBPwQIUEK"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":43,"column":1},"end":{"line":43,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"参考资料","position":{"start":{"line":43,"column":1},"end":{"line":43,"column":1}},"key":"kCOUVGr0Dt"}],"identifier":"id","label":"参考资料","html_id":"id-8","implicit":true,"key":"bHtcjyDZhF"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":45,"column":1},"end":{"line":45,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":45,"column":1},"end":{"line":45,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"link","url":"https://admin.quanttide.com/wiki/qtcloud-data-product-design-docs/","position":{"start":{"line":45,"column":1},"end":{"line":45,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"量潮数据云产品策划文档","position":{"start":{"line":45,"c